0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) Kafka 다운로드</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">wget</span> https://downloads.apache.org/kafka/2.7.0/kafka_2.13-2.7.0.tgz -P ~/Downloads\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">tar</span> zxvf ~/Downloads/kafka_2.13-2.7.0.tgz -C /usr/local\n$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">mv</span> /usr/local/kafka_2.13-2.7.0 /usr/local/kafka</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-환경변수-설정-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD%EB%B3%80%EC%88%98-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-1\" aria-label=\"2 환경변수 설정 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2) 환경변수 설정</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">vim</span> ~/.bashrc\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">KAFKA_HOME</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/usr/local/kafka\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">KAFKA_CONF_DIR</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/usr/local/kafka/config\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span><span class=\"token variable\">$KAFKA_HOME</span>/bin\n\n$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">source</span> ~/.bashrc</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"3-serverproperties-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-serverproperties-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"3 serverproperties 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3) server.properties 설정</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">vim</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$KAFKA_CONF_DIR</span>/server.properties\nbroker.id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Socket Server Settings</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">listeners</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>PLAINTEXT://:9092\nadvertised.listeners<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>PLAINTEXT://kafka-01:9092\nzookeeper.connect<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>kakfa-01:2181,kafka-02:2181,kafka-03/test</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>broker.id : 0부터 시작하고 각 서버 순서에 맞춰 0, 1, 2를 입력한다.</li>\n<li>listeners : PLAINTEXT는 말그대로 텍스트로 입력한다는 뜻으로 <code class=\"language-text\">:9092</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">0.0.0.0:9092</code>로 이해하면 된다.</li>\n<li>adverties.listeners : 마찬가지로 현재 작업 중인 서버의 호스트 네임과 9092를 입력한다.</li>\n<li>zookeeper.connect : 앞서 zookeeper를 설치하였기 때문에 연동을 위해 작성한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-kafka-실행\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-kafka-%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89\" aria-label=\"4 kafka 실행 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4) Kafka 실행</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>AWS t2.micro 로 구성할 때, swap memory가 부족하여 실행이 안되는 경우가 있다. 이 때 2GB 정도 스왑 메모리를 늘려주면 된다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ kafka-server-start.sh <span class=\"token variable\">$KAFKA_CONF_DIR</span>/server.properties\nINFO <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>broker-1-to-controller-send-thread<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>: Recorded new controller,\nfrom now on will use broker <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>kafka.server.BrokerToControllerRequestThread<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>카프카 브로커로 총 3대 설치했기 때문에 use broker 3이 나와야한다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"실행-테스트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%A4%ED%96%89-%ED%85%8C%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"실행 테스트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>실행 테스트</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>만약 실행 중인 카프카를 백그라운드로 실행하고 싶다면, -daemon 명령어로 실행 가능하다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"1-토픽-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%ED%86%A0%ED%94%BD-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"1 토픽 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) 토픽 생성</h3>\n<p>kafka-01 서버에서 테스트를 진행했다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ kafka-topics.sh --create <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --zookeeper kafka-01:2181,kafka-02:2181,kafka-03:2181/test <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --replication-factor <span class=\"token number\">3</span> --partitions <span class=\"token number\">1</span> --topic <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span>\nCreated topic test.</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"2-메세지-producer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%B8%EC%A7%80-producer\" aria-label=\"2 메세지 producer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2) 메세지 Producer</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ kafka-console-producer.sh <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --broker-list kafka-01:9092,kafka-02:9092,kafka-03:9092 <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --topic <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span>\n\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> This is a <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span> message <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> This is a <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span> message <span class=\"token number\">2</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"3-메세지-consumer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%B8%EC%A7%80-consumer\" aria-label=\"3 메세지 consumer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3) 메세지 Consumer</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ kafka-console-consumer.sh <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --bootstrap-server kafka-01:9092,kafka-02:9092,kafka-03:9092 <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --topic <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>\n    --from-beginning\nThis is a <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span> message <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\nThis is a <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">test</span> message <span class=\"token number\">2</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"AWS EC2에 Kafka Cluter 구성","date":"February 14, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Kafka/aws-ec2에-kafka-cluter-구성/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Backend/네트워크-관련-용어-정리/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"네트워크 관련 용어 정리","category":"Backend","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Hadoop/aws-ec2에-hadoop-cluster-구성/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AWS EC2에 Hadoop Cluster 구성","category":"Hadoop","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}